"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        CapabilityInformation structures with different shredding algorithm
        fields.
        """
a = objects.CapabilityInformation(shredding_algorithm=enums.
    ShreddingAlgorithm.UNSPECIFIED)
b = objects.CapabilityInformation(shredding_algorithm=enums.
    ShreddingAlgorithm.UNSUPPORTED)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
